Privacy Policy for Redcode Studios
Last Updated: 18th December, 2023
Thank you for choosing Redcode Studios! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and secure your personal information and data when you use our mobile application.

Information We Collect
Personal Information:
User-Provided Information: We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide when using Redcode Studios, such as your name, email address, or other contact information.

Device Information: We may collect information about the device you use to access Redcode Studios, including the device model, operating system, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information.

Usage Data:
We may collect information about how you interact with Redcode Studios, such as the features you use, the pages you visit, and your interactions with advertisements.
Purpose of Collecting Data
We collect and use the collected data for the following purposes:

To Provide and Maintain the Service: To deliver the features and functionalities of Redcode Studios and to ensure its proper operation.

To Improve and Personalize User Experience: To understand how users interact with Redcode Studios and to enhance user experience by tailoring content and features.

To Send Periodic Emails: If you have provided your email address, we may use it to send you updates, newsletters, and other relevant information.

How We Use Data
We may use the collected data for:

Analytics: Analyzing user behavior and trends to improve Redcode Studios' performance and user experience.

Marketing: Sending promotional materials, special offers, or other marketing communications.

Data Storage and Security
Data Storage: Your data may be stored on servers or databases hosted by third-party service providers.

Security: We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

Third-Party Services
We may use third-party services to facilitate Redcode Studios and to provide certain features. These third-party services may have their own privacy policies and practices.

Contact Information
If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy, please contact Redcode Studios at:

